        <div n="Z473A73-">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-Z473A73--headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Z473A73--headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Z473A73--headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"><hi rend="italics">Parais Deorum cultor et Infrequens</hi>,<lb/><lb/><lb/><hi rend="italics">Insenientis dum Sapientia</hi><lb/><lb/><hi rend="italics">Consultus</hi>────────────</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-Z473A73--headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Z473A73--headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Z473A73--headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-Z473A73--headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Z473A73--headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Z473A73--headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">O</hi> <hi rend="italics">S───t</hi>! why shou'd you who art wiser indeed,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-2" n="2">Than Modern Deans─── who can Write and can Read</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-3" n="3">Why shou'd you then trouble your self with such Things,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-4" n="4">As M────es, D────rs, or De────ty K────gs?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-5" n="5">If these be the Subjects of <hi rend="italics">J──────n's</hi> Pen,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-6" n="6">No more will we call him the <hi rend="italics">wisest of Men</hi>;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-7" n="7">No more we'll his Freedom on BOXES of Gold,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-8" n="8">No more we'll his Picture on <hi rend="italics">Sign Posts</hi> behold────</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-9" n="9">Why shou'd you then <hi rend="italics">J──────n</hi> trouble your Pate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-10" n="10"><hi rend="italics">With begging Epistles</hi>, or Matters of State?</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-11" n="11"><lb/>|Let the D────r be stupidly fond of his Letters,</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-12" n="12">|And dull with Impertinance trouble his Betters:</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-13" n="13">|Let him Cringe, Lie, and Flatter, and do what he can,|</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-14" n="14">|(Those Arts seldom fail to win a <hi rend="italics">Great Man</hi>)</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-15" n="15">|Let him practice 'em over and over again,</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-16" n="16">|He'll find he is a Reader of Books, not of Men.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-17" n="17"><lb/>The D────r, it may be, believes himself scanted,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-18" n="18">In poor pretty Hundreds, when Thousands he wanted;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-19" n="19">He knows that his Merits are equal to any,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-20" n="20">For who's not acquainted with D────r <hi rend="italics">D────y</hi>?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-21" n="21">I believe there are few who won't think it <hi rend="italics">Insanum</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-22" n="22">That the Doctor's possess'd of five Hundred <hi rend="italics">per Annum</hi>;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-23" n="23">Or, Merit like his, shou'd be look'd on no better,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-24" n="24">Or Answer be made to his <hi rend="italics">Excellent LETTER</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-25" n="25">These, these, are the Effects of the Times we must know,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-26" n="26">For this Way it was not some Hundreds ago.</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-27" n="27"><lb/>|But why in good Troth shou'd such Whim'eys as These,</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-28" n="28">|Be ever remember'd in <hi rend="italics">J──────n's</hi> Lays?</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-29" n="29">|No more let such Trifles your Hours Employ,</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-30" n="30">|No more let such Subjects your Virtue Destroy:</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-31" n="31">|Take this from a Friend, be <hi rend="italics">Good</hi> as you'r <hi rend="italics">Wise</hi>,</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-32" n="32">|Nor think as a Church-man, you ever will rise,</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-33" n="33">|'Till my Wise Dean you'll give over your LIBEL,|</l>
            <l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-Z473A73--line-34" n="34">|Apply to RELIGION, and think on the BIBLE.────</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
